review: I had my 3rd child on August 6th 2022 with Dr Rajsri J Shanker. I am so happy to share this review for Dr Rajsri mam. She is well experienced, friendly and very kind doctor. I can't express by words how much I was comfortable with her. She was answering and replying messages through phone anytime. That was so helpful for me instead of traveling for many times. So I am suggesting everyone that if you want to consult during your pregnancy she is the best best doctor.  Dr Rajsri mam thank you so much for everything you are done for me and my baby. You are awesome!! Thank you!!

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Doctor is very friendly and approachable. She is way too polite in explaining the issues. She is very good at counselling and make one feel quite comfortable. She tries her best to resolve the issue in the best possible way. **** ************* *** **** ************* * **** **** ** ****
Doctor was very good and explained about the problems very clearly.. doctor was very friendly and practical in explaining

I won't recommend this doctor to anyone. My sister had so much complications after the delivery. And post delivery as well there were many health issues. Her behavior is very ignorant.  

My sister had piles before the delivery. *** ****** ***** **** *** * ****** *** ******* **** *** ***** ***** *** ********** Her statement was "We will deal with the piles later". ** *** *** ** *** ** *********** **** *** ****** *** ** *** * * ******** Now because of piles and close to 15 stitches, she cannot even sit or walk properly. ** ******** ********* ****** ************** ******* ***** ************* ** *** *** ******** ** ******* * *****

She is very friendly kind, explained things well. I hope my problem will resolve soon, prescribed minimal medicines and advised necessary tests. Very ************* *** experienced , completely satisfied
